00:11:46,820 --> 00:11:48,820
There was photographic recall

271
00:11:48,820 --> 00:11:50,820
inside the children,

272
00:11:50,820 --> 00:11:53,820
I suspect because they're discussing with each other.

273
00:11:53,820 --> 00:11:55,820
A single child in front of a single computer

274
00:11:55,820 --> 00:11:57,820
will not do that.

275
00:11:57,820 --> 00:11:59,820
I have further results,

276
00:11:59,820 --> 00:12:01,820
