283
00:12:14,820 --> 00:12:16,820
after my Kuppam experiment.

284
00:12:16,820 --> 00:12:18,820
Well, you know,

285
00:12:18,820 --> 00:12:20,820
they're very vigorous people, British grandmothers.

286
00:12:20,820 --> 00:12:22,820
200 of them volunteered immediately.

287
00:12:22,820 --> 00:12:24,820
(Laughter)

288
00:12:24,820 --> 00:12:27,820
The deal was that they would give me

289
00:12:27,820 --> 00:12:29,820
one hour of broadband time,

290
00:12:29,820 --> 00:12:31,820
sitting in their homes,

291
00:12:31,820 --> 00:12:33,820
one day in a week.

292
00:12:33,820 --> 00:12:35,820
So they did that,

293
00:12:35,820 --> 00:12:37,820
and over the last two years,

294
00:12:37,820 --> 00:12:39,820
over 600 hours of instruction

295
00:12:39,820 --> 00:12:41,820
has happened over Skype,

296
00:12:41,820 --> 00:12:44,820
using what my students call the granny cloud.

297
00:12:44,820 --> 00:12:47,820
The granny cloud sits over there.

298
00:12:47,820 --> 00:12:50,820
I can beam them to whichever school I want to.

299
00:12:56,820 --> 00:12:58,820
