314
00:13:41,820 --> 00:13:44,820
(Laughter)

315
00:13:44,820 --> 00:13:47,820
(Applause)

316
00:13:47,820 --> 00:13:49,820
It's pretty simple stuff.

317
00:13:49,820 --> 00:13:51,820
This is what I'm building now --

318
00:13:51,820 --> 00:13:54,820
they're called SOLEs: Self Organized Learning Environments.

319
00:13:54,820 --> 00:13:56,820
The furniture is designed

320
00:13:56,820 --> 00:13:59,820
so that children can sit in front of big, powerful screens,

321
00:13:59,820 --> 00:14:02,820
big broadband connections, but in groups.

322
00:14:02,820 --> 00:14:05,820
If they want, they can call the granny cloud.

323
00:14:05,820 --> 00:14:07,820
This is a SOLE in Newcastle.

324
00:14:07,820 --> 00:14:09,820
The mediator is from Pune, India.

325
00:14:09,820 --> 00:14:12,820
So how far can we go? One last little bit and I'll stop.

326
00:14:12,820 --> 00:14:15,820
I went to Turin in May.

327
00:14:16,820 --> 00:14:19,820
I sent all the teachers away from my group of 10 year-old students.

328
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:23,820
I speak only English, they speak only Italian,

329
00:14:23,820 --> 00:14:25,820
so we had no way to communicate.

330
00:14:25,820 --> 00:14:28,820
I started writing English questions on the blackboard.

331
00:14:29,820 --> 00:14:31,820
The children looked at it and said, "What?"

332
00:14:31,820 --> 00:14:33,820
I said, "Well, do it."

333
00:14:33,820 --> 00:14:36,820
They typed it into Google, translated it into Italian,

334
00:14:36,820 --> 00:14:38,820
went back into Italian Google.

335
00:14:38,820 --> 00:14:41,820
Fifteen minutes later --

336
00:14:48,820 --> 00:14:51,820
next question: where is Calcutta?

337
00:14:53,820 --> 00:14:56,820
This one, they took only 10 minutes.

338
00:15:00,820 --> 00:15:03,820
I tried a really hard one then.

339
00:15:03,820 --> 00:15:06,820
Who was Pythagoras, and what did he do?

340
00:15:08,820 --> 00:15:10,820
There was silence for a while,

341
00:15:10,820 --> 00:15:12,820
then they said, "You've spelled it wrong.

342
00:15:12,820 --> 00:15:15,820
It's Pitagora."

343
00:15:19,820 --> 00:15:21,820
And then,

344
00:15:21,820 --> 00:15:23,820
in 20 minutes,

345
00:15:23,820 --> 00:15:25,820
the right-angled triangles began to appear on the screens.

346
00:15:25,820 --> 00:15:28,820
This sent shivers up my spine.

347
00:15:28,820 --> 00:15:30,820
These are 10 year-olds.

348
00:15:43,820 --> 00:15:46,820
Text: In another 30 minutes they would reach the Theory of Relativity. And then?

349
00:15:46,820 --> 00:15:48,820
(Laughter)

350
00:15:48,820 --> 00:15:57,820
(Applause)

351
00:15:57,820 --> 00:15:59,820
SM: So you know what's happened?

352
00:15:59,820 --> 00:16:01,820
I think we've just stumbled across

353
00:16:01,820 --> 00:16:03,820
a self-organizing system.

354
00:16:03,820 --> 00:16:05,820
A self-organizing system is one

355
00:16:05,820 --> 00:16:07,820
where a structure appears

356
00:16:07,820 --> 00:16:10,820
without explicit intervention from the outside.

357
00:16:10,820 --> 00:16:13,820
Self-organizing systems also always show emergence,

358
00:16:13,820 --> 00:16:15,820
which is that the system starts to do things,

359
00:16:15,820 --> 00:16:17,820
which it was never designed for.

360
00:16:17,820 --> 00:16:19,820
Which is why you react the way you do,

361
00:16:19,820 --> 00:16:22,820
because it looks impossible.

362
00:16:22,820 --> 00:16:25,820
I think I can make a guess now --

363
00:16:25,820 --> 00:16:27,820
education is self-organizing system,

364
00:16:27,820 --> 00:16:29,820
where learning is an emergent phenomenon.

365
00:16:29,820 --> 00:16:31,820
It'll take a few years to prove it, experimentally,

366
00:16:31,820 --> 00:16:33,820
but I'm going to try.

367
00:16:33,820 --> 00:16:36,820
But in the meanwhile, there is a method available.

368
00:16:36,820 --> 00:16:39,820
One billion children, we need 100 million mediators --

369
00:16:39,820 --> 00:16:41,820
there are many more than that on the planet --

370
00:16:41,820 --> 00:16:43,820
10 million SOLEs,

371
00:16:43,820 --> 00:16:46,820
180 billion dollars and 10 years.

372
00:16:47,820 --> 00:16:49,820
We could change everything.

373
00:16:49,820 --> 00:16:51,820
Thanks.

374
